{"tid":622031,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考dse瞓唔著嘅人，入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-04-08T20:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T23:44:39.000Z","uid":152123,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b13f9876f283083591b3a4f248651ba8bcdf909","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:32:07.000Z","msg":"驚咩呀，識唔識都唔會因為呢幾個鐘改變到啲乜<br />\n其實你先得十幾歲<br />\n就算直升唔到大學，唔差在個一兩年兜個圈入去架咋<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀<br />\n如果真係入唔到心儀科心儀大學<br />\n而你又覺得自己仲有機會嘅<br />\n到時就算讀asso repeat 一年都係好小事架咋<br />\n絕對好過讀住先心態去入廢u添<br />\n大把人repeat之後入咗hku添<br />\n我身邊就有兩個朋友係咁<br />\n如果你有少少錢更加唔駛愁啦<br />\n去英國讀年foundation又係一個好漢<br />\n<br />\n所以你話<br />\n其實dse真係冇咩好驚架咋<br />\n有好多時候我見兜個圈嘅人，之後條路反而走得好過直升嘅人<br />\n有啲人揀錯科 有啲人讀唔上 有啲人入錯u<br />\n你估直升就係一切咩 最多只係個一個月威水下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開學之後甚麼親戚朋友舊同學仲鬼記得你咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係你依家呢刻諗咁多嘢嚟把撚呀？</span></span><br />\n放榜先至慢慢諗啦<br />\n就算報海外大學乜乜柒柒 你等五月再諗都唔遲啦<br />\n試都未考 驚條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畀心機呀細路 人生條路仲有好長 有排你捱呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/OhQBBFi64Z81a/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FOhQBBFi64Z81a%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8d02116c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9dfc9fbac4c2d4a28e00b9a018c078decf7f055","tid":622031,"uid":179571,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53840bf28e7d1a490f1db88571f90fe2e77c6dcd","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:37:12.000Z","msg":"btw當年有一科我又係成晚冇瞓<br />\n諗住呢個鐘數瞓咗會更加攰 所以通宵唔瞓算<br />\n結果考出嚟失曬手<br />\n同埋臨考前個腦空白曬<br />\n<br />\n所以聽我話<br />\n瞓得幾多得幾多 絕對好過你唔瞓<br />\n仲有唔好飲咖啡<br />\n你聽日腎上腺素夠你撐全場<br />\n飲咗咖啡你會急尿同埋手震架"},{"pid":"d5a41a18bdb537ea3acf928e596a4f5d7b5f8c63","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:39:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吾生也有涯，而知也無涯，以有涯隨無涯，殆已！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n莊子都叫你快啲瞓教唔好諗咁多"},{"pid":"06058f07f080c974299349187849b64fc0905ba3","tid":622031,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe443ebd36e1e4d2d87debe85733567432e9cc3","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06058f07f080c974299349187849b64fc0905ba3","tid":622031,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又係龜"},{"pid":"1a572e63aeda67186d734c5d283712675f7dc86a","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bbe443ebd36e1e4d2d87debe85733567432e9cc3","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06058f07f080c974299349187849b64fc0905ba3","tid":622031,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又係龜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:46:16.000Z","msg":"我係烏大龜咁樣性格咁撚有問題就真係跳樓啦<br />\n你咁撚樣嘅心態做狀元都係死架啦<br />\n痴撚線自己考唔好公開試就上嚟打擊人<br />\n抵你一世失敗架孔乙龜"},{"pid":"10e8f6ee735042c9d8ff6ed1d8945d20ca12867e","tid":622031,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T20:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"509089066d2b1574679e37b439beade38c3d35b6","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"10e8f6ee735042c9d8ff6ed1d8945d20ca12867e","tid":622031,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a572e63aeda67186d734c5d283712675f7dc86a","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bbe443ebd36e1e4d2d87debe85733567432e9cc3","tid":622031,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTi